<item>
            <title>[HIVE-7063] Optimize for the Top N within a Group use case</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HIVE-7063</link>
                <project id="12310843" key="HIVE">Hive</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It is common to rank within a Group/Partition and then only return the Top N entries within each Group.&lt;br/&gt;
With Streaming mode for Windowing, we should push the post filter on the rank into the Windowing processing as a Limit expression.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
